OL,3,CWomen are more likely to be
OL,4,Covercharged at garages - here's how to
OL,5,Csteer clear
OL,7,FITV News' Consumer Editor Chris Choi
OL,8,Fbreaks down how to avoid getting a
OL,9,Fworse deal for work done on your car.
OL,11,FNew data appears to confirm what many
OL,12,Fwomen drivers have long suspected -
OL,13,Fthey get a worse deal from the motor
OL,14,Ftrade.
OL,16,FOne thousand female motorists took
OL,17,Fpart in the research, which has been
OL,18,Fgiven exclusively to ITV News. One
OL,19,Finsider says women are treated like
OL,20,F"an easy target" for overcharging.
