OL,3,CWomen are more likely to be
OL,4,Covercharged at garages - here's how to
OL,5,Csteer clear
OL,7,FAs I did my background research for
OL,8,Fthis assignment, I spoke to a number
OL,9,Fof motor industry experts and I've
OL,10,Fdistilled down what I think are their
OL,11,Fmost important tips:
OL,13,FDo your homework
OL,15,FGet some sort of idea about what might
OL,16,Fbe wrong with the vehicle and likely
OL,17,Fcosts before you go to the garage. It
OL,18,Fmeans you can have a much more
OL,19,Feffective conversation with the
OL,20,Fmechanic.
