OL,3,CWomen are more likely to be
OL,4,Covercharged at garages - here's how to
OL,5,Csteer clear
OL,7,FShop around
OL,9,FIt is the oldest rule in the book, but
OL,10,Ffor some reason, we don't often do it
OL,11,Fwith garages. We tend to choose what
OL,12,Fis geographically close or has been
OL,13,Frecommended.
OL,15,FOnce you get a quote from a garage you
OL,16,Fcan call others and see what they'd
OL,17,Fcharge. Find out what sort of
OL,18,Fguarantees their work comes with.
OL,20,FHold onto receipts
