OL,3,CWomen are more likely to be
OL,4,Covercharged at garages - here's how to
OL,5,Csteer clear
OL,7,FThe new survey of 1000 female
OL,8,Fmotorists given exclusively to ITV
OL,9,FNews by Carly Motor Diagnostics shows
OL,10,F77% don't trust garages, and more than
OL,11,Fhalf believe they will be treated
OL,12,Fbetter if they are accompanied by a
OL,13,Fman.
OL,15,FOf those surveyed 61% now support the
OL,16,Fidea of a specific new law to protect
OL,17,Ffemale customers from overcharging in
OL,18,Fthis sector.
